title: Tore Up Over You
lyrics:
Ever since you've been gone
I just cry the whole night long
Since the day you said good-bye
You hurt me so, no lie, no lie
Tore up over you and just can't find my way


Tore up, yeah, yeah, yeah, tore up

Tore up, yeah, yeah, yeah, tore up

Tore up over you and I just can't find my way



You never loved me like you told me so

If you did, how could you go?

It was you, not me that left

And went away with someone else

Tore up over you and I just can't find my way



Tore up, yeah, yeah, yeah, tore up

Tore up, yeah, yeah, yeah, tore up

Tore up over you and I just can't find my way



Tell me what did I do

To make you go away

Tell me what can I do

To make you come back to stay

I'm tore up over you and I just can't find my way



Tore up, yeah, yeah, yeah, tore up

Tore up, yeah, yeah, yeah, tore up

Tore up over you and I just can't find my way
